; Finance scraper (SPEC §12.2, M6; unfrozen D-049/050/051). Two steps in one
; oneshot: (1) Node logs into Mizrahi/Max/Cal READ-ONLY and writes a CSV per
; provider to /var/lib/family-inc/finance; (2) Python ingests those CSVs and is
; the only thing that writes the Sheet (D-016 — Node scrapes, Python writes).
; Puppeteer headless, NO Xvfb (anti-bot is clean for this mix — the 2026
; Cloudflare wall is Isracard/Amex, not ingested, §12.2). Silent lane: balances
; surface in the weekly briefing Money section + dashboard drawer, never an
; alert. TimeoutStartSec/MemoryMax bound a stuck browser; OnFailure raises the
; fail-flag the next digest reports (§10.2). A creds-missing run or a provider
; OTP re-challenge fails loud (scrape exit 1, or the _scrape_errors.json marker
; that finance_ingest.py re-raises after persisting the good data).
[Unit]
Description=Family inc. finance scraper (Mizrahi/Max/Cal → Finance-Transactions)
OnFailure=family-fail-flag@%n.service

[Service]
Type=oneshot
User=familyinc
WorkingDirectory=/opt/family-inc
EnvironmentFile=-/etc/family-inc/env
Environment=FAMILY_INC_FINANCE_DIR=/var/lib/family-inc/finance
StateDirectory=family-inc/finance
; Owner-only state: the dir holds the device-trust browser profiles (live bank
; session cookies) and the transaction CSVs. UMask=0077 keeps the CSVs 0600 too.
StateDirectoryMode=0700
UMask=0077
TimeoutStartSec=600
MemoryMax=1500M
ExecStart=/usr/bin/node automation/finance/scrape.js
ExecStart=/usr/local/bin/uv run --no-sync python automation/finance_ingest.py
NoNewPrivileges=true
